##For any quary, Please find the contact details on the Readme file.

1-Install Reference genome"
    Go to (http://hgdownload.soe.ucsc.edu/goldenPath/hg19/chromosomes/)
    Download Chr1-22 , X , Y and MT
    use cat command on lunix terminal to concatenate all chromosomes in the same order.
2-Install BWA for (http://bio-bwa.sourceforge.net/)
3-Index the reference genome by :
    bwa index -a bwtsw PathToReferenceGnome 
4-Install samtools from (http://samtools.sourceforge.net/)
5-Install Picard-tools from (https://broadinstitute.github.io/picard/)
6-Install GATK from (https://github.com/broadinstitute/gatk/releases)
7-Install RTG-Tools from (https://github.com/RealTimeGenomics/rtg-tools)
8-Install latest release of GIAB Data set from (https://www.nist.gov/programs-projects/genome-bottle)
